---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 289
  - Title: The Glory of the World
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Spiritual Master
---
Our Art is good and precious, nor can any one become a partaker of it,
unless it be revealed to him by God, or unless he be taught by a
skilled Master. It is a treasure such as the whole world cannot buy.
